{"tid":2283361,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 黎明之戰再現","createTime":"2020-11-12T13:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T15:04:13.000Z","uid":132888,"like":26,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"13d511e3a281138dd801241a8b82ca26b2d7fbdc","tid":2283361,"uid":132888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:28:45.000Z","msg":"唔好意思呃左大家入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋係一班香港嘅年青人，唔喺任何知名或業內人士，只喺幾個普通，無名嘅年青人。<br />\n<br />\n我哋最近構思咗一副以「貓城抗爭」為題材嘅Boardgame--《無名貓:黎明之戰》，仲放左上Kickstarter眾籌，如果成功嘅就可以進入生產階段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/freedomsoulsgame/371192491?ref=project_build\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Ffreedomsoulsgame%2F371192491%3Fref%3Dproject_build&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2839c3c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/freedomsoulsgame/371192491?ref=project_build</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sf66qOk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsf66qOk.png&h=bed1a3fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋本身做呢個遊戲嘅用意係想將我哋自己嘅一啲見聞同想法向大家分享。<br />\n同時係呢個亂世入邊，歷史已經漸漸地被奸人篡改，所以我地希望製作呢個Game記錄低呢場運動，大家未來可以憑住隻Game去回憶呢個時代，亦可以同你地嘅下一代一邊玩一邊教育佢地，呈現最真實嘅歷史。<br />\n咁當然，我哋亦都會保證呢個係一個好玩嘅遊戲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現實係面對敵方較強嘅情況下，我哋需要集合每一點嘅力量，需要喺每一個細節堅持，遊戲亦然。我哋希望可以鼓勵大家做自己能力可以做到嘅嘢，譬如冇Twitter嘅就開返個(唔好講笑，真係好多人冇)<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋想支持本地嘅生態圈，由印刷到運輸，我哋全部會選用香港本土公司。因為要堅持我哋自己嘅初衷，製作一副純Made in HK嘅Boardgame，成本係一個不可避免嘅問題。所以我哋都會盡能力係市面上搵唔同嘅渠道同協助，盡量令成本降低。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後岔開少少講下，我哋一直都無用「手足」「黃店/經濟圈」呢啲字眼，因為我哋唔想大家一見到呢啲字眼就盲目跟從，無論件事好定唔好都要先思考下背後嘅真正意義；亦都想大家知道係大眾視線底下有一群默默付出嘅無名之士。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋將來亦希望可以做到一個媒介甚至係一個平台，等更多香港嘅年青人有個自主工作、自給自足、向上游嘅機會，唔洗不斷做啲低技術工作、做死一世打工仔；可以為生活而生活，而非生存。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家願意支持我地又或者想了解更多關於隻Game嘅資訊，歡迎去以下呢啲渠道，多謝各位香港人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/freedomsoulsgame/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ffreedomsoulsgame%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=ff9e493e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/freedomsoulsgame/</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/freedomsouls3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffreedomsouls3&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=c088f44f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/freedomsouls3</a><br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E8%B2%93%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0-FreedomSouls-105196828064542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25B2%2593%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25B9%258B%25E6%2588%25B0-FreedomSouls-105196828064542&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=71db082f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E8%B2%93%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%8B%E6%88%B0-FreedomSouls-105196828064542</a>"},{"pid":"53298a87dc47ae7efb19abe510775a2145b52bd4","tid":2283361,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896a7464c12b667afdb8ac47ae48968d4ffbd68d","tid":2283361,"uid":22591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T13:41:34.000Z","ms